This tells the user to: (1) run `npm run blindfold -- proxy` leaving it running, (2) optionally start `npm run dashboard` which serves `http://127.0.0.1:8799`, and (3) point their agent at base URL `http://127.0.0.1:8787/v1` with the sentinel API key `__BLINDFOLD__`. The note about `--start` repeats that passing it would have auto-spawned the proxy instead of printing these instructions.

