> "SECURITY: this module never logs a secret value. It only reads names from .env and delegates the single plaintext touch to `registerSecret` (the one audit-critical path). The .env rewrite operates on line text, not values."

So classification is purely name-based; values flow only through `registerSecret` imported from `./register.ts`, which is the audit-critical substitution point.

