The script operates on the tenant-level `secrets` map in TDX — Blindfold stores its one-file plaintext path there (the in-enclave substitution target). Granting the proxy contract read on `secrets` is what allows the enclave to resolve the plaintext mapping at execution time. This script is a manual recovery/grant step, not part of normal test flow.

